平方米<br />\n2. 中央草坪：9800 平方米<br />\n3. 藍亭廣場：1435 平方米<br />\n4. 籃球場：1050 平方米<br />\n5. 通道：1931 平方米<br />\n<br />\n5 個面積總和：43293 平方米<br />\n<br />\n以每平方米 2.8 人計算：2.8 人/米 x 43293 平方米 = 121220 人。<br />\n以每平方米 2.5 人計算：2.5 人/米 x 43293 平方米 = 108233 人。"},{"pid":"4e1e51cf02b16e174ebf33dc8802c102dfe3e804","tid":270724,"uid":66736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:47:25.000Z","msg":"估計無去既人高達六百萬"},{"pid":"3758d46d3b51fa659a8a810c1383cd51f09bb199","tid":270724,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:47:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本土派搞成咁我估好多人都回流</blockquote><br />\n老實講寧願維園少個足球場<br />\n尖沙咀爆晒<br />\n本土派自己唔爭氣冇辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0dff0d901ffe9d7ef1a13c5ded6b175b0e7d3b8","tid":270724,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:48:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>坐滿6個足球場 + 少部份草地，<br />\n<br />\n估計11萬人</blockquote><br />\nrthk報導<br />\n支聯會在維園舉行的六四燭光悼念集會，主席何俊仁表示有約11萬人參與晚會，坐滿6個足球場及<span style=\"color: red;\">至少一半</span>草地範圍。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n按HKU統計科學方法:<br />\n12,134人"},{"pid":"46151d5d612f2b62633c0370b125d005c38ef91f","tid":270724,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:48:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本土派搞成咁我估好多人都回流</blockquote><br />\n正常,唔通仲痴埋去垃圾本土派度咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fec8f26fcdfd67fa209d181fcd570979b20fffd","tid":270724,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:49:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>本土派搞成咁我估好多人都回流</blockquote><br />\n老實講寧願維園少個足球場<br />\n尖沙咀爆晒<br />\n本土派自己唔爭氣冇辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大中華根種左百幾年<br />\n本土派近五年先慢慢起步<br />\n想點呀"},{"pid":"08e6b09202db32adf0cb446476da261977adfd6e","tid":270724,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T13:49:25.000Z","m